|--------|----------|-------------------|
| Warehouse | Depo tesisi | Name, Code, Address, Type, TimeZone |
| Zone | Depo bolgesi (bulk, pick, staging) | Name, Type, WarehouseId, Temperature |
| Location | Raf konumu | Code (A-01-02-03), ZoneId, Type, Capacity, CurrentWeight |
| Product | Urun master verisi | SKU, Name, UOM, Weight, Dimensions, BarcodeList |
