| InboundOrder | Mal kabul siparisi | ASN#, SupplierId, ExpectedDate, Status, Lines[] |
| OutboundOrder | Sevkiyat siparisi | OrderNumber, CustomerId, Priority, Status, Lines[] |
| Wave | Dalga (toplu toplama) | WaveNumber, Orders[], Status, PickStrategy |
