## Is Kurallari

### Stok Yonetimi
- Her stok hareketi `StockMovement` kaydı olusturur (audit trail)
- Negatif stok YASAK (exception: adjustment with approval)
- Lot tracking: gida/ilac icin ZORUNLU (FEFO)
- Serial tracking: yuksek degerli urunler icin
- Stok durumu: Available, Reserved, Damaged, Quarantine, InTransit

### FIFO/FEFO Kurali
```
Picking sirasinda urun secimi:
├── Gida/ilac? -> FEFO (ExpiryDate ASC, en yakin tarih once)
├── Normal urun? -> FIFO (ReceivedDate ASC, en eski once)
├── Ozel kural? -> Customer-specific (lot preference)
└── Ayni tarih? -> Location proximity (en yakin konum)
```

### Konum Adresleme (Location Code)
```
Format: {Zone}-{Aisle}-{Rack}-{Level}
Ornek: A-01-02-03 = Zone A, Koridor 1, Raf 2, Seviye 3
       RECV-STAGE-01 = Receiving staging alani 1
       SHIP-DOCK-03 = Shipping dock 3
```

## Status Akislari

### Inbound Order Lifecycle
```
Draft -> Confirmed -> Arrived -> Receiving -> Quality Check
   -> Putaway -> Completed
   -> Partially Received (kismi kabul)
   -> Rejected (kalite red)
```

### Outbound Order Lifecycle
```
Draft -> Confirmed -> Wave Assigned -> Picking -> Picked
   -> Packing -> Packed -> Loading -> Shipped -> Delivered
   -> Short Pick (eksik toplama)
   -> Cancelled
```

### Task Lifecycle
```
Created -> Assigned -> InProgress -> Completed
   -> Paused (mola, oncelik degisimi)
   -> Cancelled
   -> Failed (sorun bildirimi)
```

## KPI'lar
| KPI | Formul | Hedef |
|-----|--------|-------|
| Order Accuracy | Hatasiz siparis / Toplam siparis | > %99.5 |
| On-Time Shipment | Zamaninda sevk / Toplam sevk | > %98 |
| Inventory Accuracy | Sayim dogru konum / Toplam konum | > %99 |
| Putaway Time | Ort. yerlestirme suresi | < 15 dk |
| Pick Rate | Urun/saat/operator | > 100 |
| Dock-to-Stock | Mal kabul -> raf suresi | < 4 saat |
| Space Utilization | Kullanilan alan / Toplam alan | > %85 |
| Damage Rate | Hasarli urun / Toplam urun | < %0.5 |
